<subSubSection pageId="98" pageNumber="99" type="use">
<paragraph pageId="98" pageNumber="99">Use.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="98" pageNumber="99">
Fruits are reported to be edible, juicy, and thirst-quenching (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="98" pageNumber="99">P.R.O. Bally 12989</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
